Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:06.17,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,King Joseph of Gallia's recent attack
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:09.19,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,came completely out of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:12.83,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,It was an unspeakable attempt
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:15.76,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,to turn Romalia and many \Ninnocent people to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:19.02,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,We have been shaken by fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.02,0:00:20.87,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Being turned to ash is unbearable!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:22.57,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,If you're turned to ash,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.57,0:00:25.56,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,you can't even admire a woman's rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:27.91,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,And that is boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:29.89,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Truly boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.72,0:00:32.73,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.73,0:00:38.22,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,these heroes stopped King \NJoseph's delusional plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:42.95,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,They are the ones who \Nsaved Halkeginia, no,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:45.19,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,the entire world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.78,0:00:49.10,CRZero,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Long live Tristain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:51.28,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly relieved that \Nyou made it back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.68,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Now let us eat, drink, and be merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:56.77,CRZero,Osmond,0000,0000,0000,,Let us enjoy these hours of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:00.73,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.73,0:01:02.17,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:04.78,CRZero,Lionel,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:06.94,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone's getting a reward, \Nit would be Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.36,0:01:10.41,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's the one \Nwho saved Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:11.89,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.89,0:01:12.79,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.79,0:01:14.75,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Even an estate wouldn't be too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:16.13,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An estate...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:19.73,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't buy you a real mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:21.74,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe not now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:24.46,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:03.03,Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(585,1)}The Queen's Reward
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:08.48,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Guiche, I'm so glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:10.54,CRZero,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:12.47,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.91,0:03:17.17,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was your prayers \Nthat delivered me home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.42,0:03:20.08,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to let that go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:21.98,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.98,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to look at it \Nlike some sort of disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:28.00,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it seems to have gotten worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:32.80,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:34.97,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,M-Montmorency...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:38.63,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you kiss another \Ngirl in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.14,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.43,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,I had something on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:42.70,CRZero,Guiche,0000,0000,0000,,and she was just helping \Nme get it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.14,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,That's the lamest excuse ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.21,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,This is it, I won't \Nforgive you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:52.11,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for saving us in Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.04,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.26,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito is very grateful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.57,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,He is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:07.32,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I'll find my familiar soon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:09.36,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,and have a relationship like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:12.03,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but we fight all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:12.97,CRZero,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:16.73,CRZero,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania, may I ask you for a dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.05,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,You want to dance with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.05,0:04:20.51,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave you two alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.29,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,L-Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:23.90,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Tiffa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:25.76,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:27.11,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,I can't dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:29.50,CRZero,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:31.16,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.45,CRZero,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad when people \Ndon't know their places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:37.63,CRZero,Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen your face recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.66,CRZero,Girl C,0000,0000,0000,,Go wash your face and then come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:45.59,CRZero,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffania, you deserve a lord
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:49.63,CRZero,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,with much higher standing \Nthan that scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:51.44,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,B-Beatrice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.75,CRZero,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,I swear on the honor \Nof my family, Guldenhorf,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.17,CRZero,Beatrice,0000,0000,0000,,to find you someone much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:05:00.81,CRZero,Tiffania,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, you really don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:04.66,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering where you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.42,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You should try some \Nof this food, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.63,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this all looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:10.79,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.81,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,These were really great, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.47,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're a big fan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:16.93,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,of melons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.93,0:05:19.07,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Melons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:21.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't know what you're \Ntalking about, Malicorne!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:23.51,CRZero,Malicorne,0000,0000,0000,,Bye then, little lemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:27.24,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What was he saying about melons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:28.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.90,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.28,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:38.72,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,This was the first song we danced to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:53.36,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair and your dress \Nare the same as that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:55.67,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Took you long enough to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.71,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You can be so dense sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:05:59.57,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:07.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy we can dance like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.20,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't be dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:10.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not being dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.35,0:06:13.50,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like my heart would stop
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.30,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,when I heard that they took you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:16.90,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I kept wondering what I'd do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:18.19,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,if anything happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:19.06,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.66,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I truly understood
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.66,0:06:23.83,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,how important you are to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:25.83,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I never want to leave your side again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.34,0:06:30.57,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you always.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.44,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have to be big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:36.91,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's buy a house together someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.34,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,One for just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.97,0:06:40.95,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:42.62,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:46.12,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you really insist, I suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.79,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I can go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.36,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:55.80,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you forever, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:57.92,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:06:59.53,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:07.08,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.45,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:13.12,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:20.92,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hang on, you can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.47,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:25.17,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never letting you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.46,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,We're together forever now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.32,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:36.00,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.10,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:39.83,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You were going to try to \Nget him in his sleep again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:43.23,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,You know me too well, Miss Vallière!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:46.79,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I warmed your bed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:49.00,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,But if you would like it to be warmer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:52.25,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I will warm you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:57.02,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, but thanks for \Nyour concern, Siesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:59.18,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Concern, my eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.76,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You've got this totally perverted grin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:02.33,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:07.51,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But, I mean, I am a guy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:09.43,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.30,0:08:16.47,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. Why are all guys like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.80,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,It's so idiotic,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:22.50,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,the way they run to this \Ngirl and that girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:24.72,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.50,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.38,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that \Nthis is so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:30.75,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,We've really made it home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:32.41,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.54,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,The only one missing is Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.00,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what she's doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.40,0:08:41.95,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We had just gotten back here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:44.42,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,and then she took off for Gallia again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:46.80,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,She did receive a letter asking
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:48.97,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,for her immediate return quite urgently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.69,0:08:52.64,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she's not getting \Nmixed up in some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:55.58,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,She can take care of herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.32,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:09.77,CRZero,Castelmore,0000,0000,0000,,Can this really mend her broken heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:13.10,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:17.03,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the medicine that will \Nmend your mother's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.24,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.76,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did you become his pawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:30.33,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There was something I had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:33.28,CRZero,Bidalsha,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's all I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:53.43,CRZero,Percerin,0000,0000,0000,,My Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:54.90,CRZero,Castelmore,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Orléans!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.77,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:06.08,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte... It's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:10.09,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:26.24,CRZero,Knights,0000,0000,0000,,One, two! One, two! One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:28.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't have to be big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.64,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's buy a house together someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.70,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:33.82,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:35.37,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:36.25,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,With Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.82,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Tiffa's so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:43.03,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she was on top of Saito like so
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.06,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,and trying to kiss him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:45.79,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:48.83,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,And when Malicorne saw them,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.91,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,he started talking about melons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:55.33,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,If she's melons, would I be coconuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:57.93,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay idle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.57,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,And I'd put the living room here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.36,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This would be the banquet hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:05.21,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,And here I'd have our dinner parties...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.33,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need to have \Nsome guest rooms, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.62,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:13.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,The master bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:15.37,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:16.80,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:21.75,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't think about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:24.30,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That has to wait until we're married!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.86,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But we're going to live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:28.73,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I can't think about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.84,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière, \Nsomething terrible happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.95,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong, Siesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:34.57,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:37.09,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard about how Miss Westwood
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:38.34,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,made a move on Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.87,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What? Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:40.89,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:42.99,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,They were saying something \Nabout melons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.98,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what the whole \Nmelon thing was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:51.82,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I can live \Nwith my pineapples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:54.98,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I know I've got lemons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.83,0:11:56.70,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:59.13,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:01.24,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,What is this supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.19,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell by looking at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:07.01,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It's the house where Saito \Nand I are going to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:09.73,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Miss Vallière!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:13.57,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,You should buy a house \Nwith Saito to prevent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.53,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Westwood from seducing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:16.25,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,A house with Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.67,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.18,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,You want to eliminate as \Nmany rivals as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:22.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:25.35,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to find a house where we can
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:27.77,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,both live before something bad happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:36.87,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to come look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.51,0:12:41.34,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,This mansion's kitchen looks \Nso spacious and convenient!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:45.99,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Your cooking is great \Nno matter what, Siesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:48.71,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:49.89,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:53.99,CRZero,Realtor,0000,0000,0000,,But this mansion was designed by
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:57.49,CRZero,Realtor,0000,0000,0000,,that one very famous architect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:13:00.29,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't like it, I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.02,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:03.35,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.63,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:07.84,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here anyway, Siesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.06,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This house is for me and Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.31,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This is none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:17.49,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,But if Saito moves, \NI have to move with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.74,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Who decided that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.01,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Her majesty did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:26.38,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Henrietta made me \NSaito's personal maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.41,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Which means you can't fire me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.09,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Let us three
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:34.73,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,just continue to enjoy each \Nother's company, Miss Vallière!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.56,CRZero,Realtor,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for a \Nplace for three people,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:38.98,CRZero,Realtor,0000,0000,0000,,how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:40.23,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:43.61,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So that was your motive \Nfor looking for a place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.67,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't Siesta come \Nlive with us anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:49.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to find a \Ngood worker like Siesta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:52.50,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:55.62,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:57.02,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, come look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.59,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That does look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:02.92,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's got a big bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.41,CRZero,Realtor,0000,0000,0000,,Big enough for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.49,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,For two? Oh, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.63,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What's so great about this room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.63,0:14:12.84,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:18.24,CRZero,Scarron,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying you \Ndidn't find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:22.29,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, first she insisted \Non finding a place,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.61,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,then she did nothing but complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.61,0:14:25.74,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we couldn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:27.90,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I am the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.56,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with looking until we find
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:31.07,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,something I'm happy with?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:33.00,CRZero,Jessica,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:35.20,CRZero,Jessica,0000,0000,0000,,You should just go ahead and make sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.71,CRZero,Jessica,0000,0000,0000,,before you get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.46,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:41.23,CRZero,Jessica,0000,0000,0000,,That you're physically suited \Nto each other, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.40,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.67,0:14:46.55,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll do that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.87,CRZero,Scarron,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy to be popular \Nwith the ladies, huh, Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:51.60,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say I'm popular, exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.39,CRZero,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,We all heard, Saito! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:56.30,CRZero,Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,Spectacular!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.34,CRZero,Girl C,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.78,0:14:59.44,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.76,0:15:00.95,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:02.25,CRZero,Scarron,0000,0000,0000,,They're talking about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:04.47,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,The Queen's Knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:05.30,CRZero,Scarron,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.60,CRZero,Scarron,0000,0000,0000,,The play is extremely popular \Nwith the townspeople.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:12.69,CRZero,Jessica,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me, evil and \Ncruel army of Gallia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.93,CRZero,Scarron,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.27,CRZero,Jessica,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Incompetent King Joseph!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.64,CRZero,Jessica,0000,0000,0000,,Our beloved Queen has sent me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:23.13,CRZero,Jessica,0000,0000,0000,,to face any enemy of the Brimir faith!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:27.47,CRZero,Jessica,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Swordsman of the \NWind, Hiligil Sartom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.67,0:15:31.01,CRZero,Scarron,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, Hiligil Sartom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.61,CRZero,Scarron,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.97,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Is Hiligil supposed to be me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:38.48,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:41.41,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.69,CRZero,Scarron,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:45.97,CRZero,Jessica,0000,0000,0000,,Now for the final blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:49.56,CRZero,Jessica,0000,0000,0000,,I finished him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:52.54,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What a horrible play.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.52,CRZero,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,You were wonderful, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.50,CRZero,Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,Truly great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:16:01.22,CRZero,Scarron,0000,0000,0000,,By now, Saito's the hero \Nwho saved His Holiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:04.49,CRZero,Jessica,0000,0000,0000,,All the town girls are in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.48,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,The town girls are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:08.21,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,...in love with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.89,0:16:11.61,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to find a mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.90,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,...before we get even more rivals!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:14.69,CRZero,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.59,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Be queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:18.54,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:21.44,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Castelmore thinks so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:24.10,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Castelmore was loyal to your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.31,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,the Lord of Orléans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.74,0:16:30.86,CRZero,Castelmore,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Gallia has \Nforgotten its pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:32.18,CRZero,Castelmore,0000,0000,0000,,It lies in confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:35.46,CRZero,Castelmore,0000,0000,0000,,The people have forgotten how to smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:38.21,CRZero,Castelmore,0000,0000,0000,,and nobody knows what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.18,CRZero,Castelmore,0000,0000,0000,,This country needs you on the throne
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.47,CRZero,Castelmore,0000,0000,0000,,to make itself whole again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:44.35,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:49.95,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something your \Nfather told me long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:53.69,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "We must make this land better."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:55.63,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,This land?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:56.66,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.15,0:17:00.61,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,And I would like to honor that memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:05.27,CRZero,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,You will agree, won't you, Charlotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:12.44,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We've been searching \Nfor three days now. Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:15.93,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,How far do we have to go \Nto find a decent mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:20.12,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you have to \Nbicker about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:23.39,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's no wonder we haven't \Nfound anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:26.15,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you saying this is all my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:27.05,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:27.99,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:30.08,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Agnès?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:32.26,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.85,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Henrietta wishes to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:37.77,CRZero,Agnès,0000,0000,0000,,Please go to her court at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:43.57,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I got you into danger in Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:45.31,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.46,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,This is not to make up for that, but I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.01,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,wanted you to know I was sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.19,0:17:52.28,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:55.29,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I received a message from Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:59.20,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Tabitha will become \Nthe new ruler of Gallia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:00.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:01.86,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:04.49,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose officially it \Nwill be Queen Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:08.57,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that's what \Nshe really wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:13.96,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I worry about that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:16.11,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, it was Tabitha's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:19.40,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she gave it plenty of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:21.61,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she did...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:26.01,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we enjoy this \Nwhile it's still warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:30.86,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored that you \Nreceived us like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:32.96,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. It was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:37.83,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Saito, for all you \Nhave done to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.11,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,you would be entitled to a reward
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:41.80,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,worthy of your status as chevalier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:42.87,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,However, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:45.94,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,...the Tristain coffers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:48.18,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. I don't need a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.63,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,No, I must insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:54.50,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's meager, \Nbut I'd like to give you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.91,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,a small fiefdom from my own holdings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:18:58.92,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fiefdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.36,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's a fiefdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:02.41,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If you are given a fiefdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.15,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,it would mean that you would become
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:06.17,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,that holding's king! Its lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,A lord? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:12.90,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,There's a piece of land in western \N Tristainia called De Ornierés.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.61,0:19:16.08,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you will like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:19.25,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't this too much for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:21.45,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I would feel guilty not rewarding
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:23.27,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,him in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:26.11,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, this is all I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:39.29,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,There's absolutely nothing here, \Nas far as the eye can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:44.23,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Could there possibly \Nbe a mansion out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:54.81,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.81,0:19:57.28,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,We're trying to find \NDe Ornierés fiefdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.06,CRZero,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Then you've found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.86,0:20:02.15,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You mean this wasteland is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:04.04,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What about the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:05.62,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.26,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a haunted mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:17.36,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,The princess sure likes to joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:21.67,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,They do say your home is your castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:23.58,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the princess did \Ngive it to me out of the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.84,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,goodness of her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:25.70,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Now hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.77,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you actually \Nwant to live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:32.44,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,You can go back if you don't \Nlike it, Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:37.06,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Saito and I can live here all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.45,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I will live here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:40.76,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am going to live here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.79,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Would you rather sleep on \Nhis right or on his left?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,There are a million other rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:50.75,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,so go sleep somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:54.02,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm scared to sleep here alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:55.37,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,What if a ghost comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:21:00.34,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we all just get along?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:08.51,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.28,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:14.49,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Moving in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:22.95,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You put the coronation on hold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:23.75,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:27.21,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Tabitha, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.86,0:21:33.90,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:35.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:39.94,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,It is very late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:42.09,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight, Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:45.62,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:47.21,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,We're finally in our own mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:50.76,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This is even worse than \Nbeing at the academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:29.45,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, this stinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.45,0:23:31.74,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This mansion was supposed to \Nbe just for me and Saito,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.74,0:23:33.61,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,but all these people keep \Ngetting in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.61,0:23:35.74,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Tune in next time for \N"The Maidens of De Ornierés."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:40.16,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the princess kissing Saito?!
